result.execSummary:
The defendant Steven M Dennis was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Steven M Dennis is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Steven M Dennis was found guilty of Possession of Narcotic Drugs, a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(am).
